<tr><td>Yes, certainly, with pleasure.</td>
<td>Jes, certe, kun plezuro.</td></tr>
<tr><td>You are very kind. When will you come?</td>
<td>Vi estas tre ĝentila. Kiam vi alvenos?</td></tr>
<tr><td>What is the date to-day? I will come in a few
