<tr><td><span class="pagenum">153</span> I will visit you any time that is agreeable to you.</td>
<td>Mi vizitos vin tiam kiam estos agrable al vi.</td></tr>
<tr><td>Come as often as possible—every day if you like.</td>
<td>Venu kiel eble plej ofte, ĉiutage, se vi volos.</td></tr>
<tr><td>I will do that willingly.</td>
<td>Tre volonte mi faros tion.</td></tr>
<tr><td>I think I will come to you to-morrow, and from now I will
